metadata.description: The Locker Room pass is an exclusive all access NFT which unlocks the EvolveNFTs product suite and locker room community. The limited edition of 456 total genesis NFTs will be free to mint and give you immediate access to benefits ranging from; Evolve Monthly Institutional Web3 Report ($250 per month, free with your locker room pass), Evolve Company Deep Dives & Alpha Reports, Exclusive WL spots and early access to upcoming projects, Evolve community chats, staking rewards, giveaways, discounts within our growing partnership network, access to professional athletes, and a community of developers and business people.
metadata.name: EvolveNFTs Locker Room Pass - Coming Soon
